
To install LogZilla, simply change to the scripts/ directory and run the install.pl script.
You can also use an answer file for installs by folling the guide here:
https://www.assembla.com/spaces/LogZillaWiki/wiki/RC_File

Ubuntu Users, quick install:
https://www.assembla.com/spaces/LogZillaWiki/wiki/Ubuntu


